+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${PKGSTEM} on OpenBSD
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Install the browser extension from:
https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/addon/browserpass-ce/

Add the following entries to ${SYSCONFDIR}/firefox/unveil.main (or
${SYSCONFDIR}/firefox-esr/unveil.main if using firefox-esr):

${TRUEPREFIX}/share/browserpass/browserpass rx
${TRUEPREFIX}/share/browserpass r
